      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of the S54-powered icon. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six delivers linear power through six individual throttle bodies, optimized by a meticulously maintained double-VANOS system. The chassis remains structurally pristine with documented subframe reinforcement and fresh bushings throughout. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M Variable Differential Lock. Every factory VIN tag is present, and the suspension geometry remains true to OEM specifications. Performance is sharp, with the hydraulic steering rack providing unparalleled feedback and the ventilated rotors showing zero lip.",
